manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.valcourgames.walletwatch.android.HomeActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.title: BTC Wallet Watch
playstore_details.description:
Track and view the balance of any cryptocurrency wallet.  Works for Bitcoin, Bitcoin Cash, Bitcoin Gold, Litecoin, Ethereum, and Ethereum Classic.

- Displays Wallet Balance and Total Received
- Save as many wallet address as you would like
- Add your own custom name for each wallet
- Enter public addresses with QR code scanner
- View the last 50 wallet transactions
- Converts BTC, BCH, BTG, LTC, ETH, and ETC to estimated US Dollar value
- Also convert to Japanese Yen, South Korean Won, Euro, Hong Kong Dollar, Philippine Peso, Indonesian Rupiah, and British Pound
- Displays total value of all saved addresses
- Supports xpub bitcoin addresses

Uses:
blockchain.info
cryptocompare.com
blockdozer.com
btgexplorer.com
insight.litecore.io
blockcypher.com
gastracker.io
